This is Perl module KiokuDB::Backend::Riak.

INSTALLATION

KiokuDB::Backend::Riak installation is straightforward. If your CPAN shell is set up,
you should just be able to do

    % cpan KiokuDB::Backend::Riak

Download it, unpack it, then build it as per the usual:

    % perl Makefile.PL
    % make && make test

Then install it:

    % make install

DOCUMENTATION

KiokuDB::Backend::Riak documentation is available as in POD. So you can do:

    % perldoc KiokuDB::Backend::Riak

to read the documentation online with your favorite pager.

